attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Known affectionately as THE LOFT, this Fort Point Channel 1880’s industrial loft Landmark’s treasure thrives today as an eclectic residential brick & beam at the cornerstone of the cutting-edge Seaport! Versatility is paramount within this sanctuary that begs an exhale upon entry to the sprawling 65’ open concept lined with oversized windows rich in natural light showcasing an urban vista framed by 12’ ceilings. A sophisticated design with both privacy & community at heart reveals itself thru sliding walls that curate spaces for maximum flow & efficiency. Purposed today as a 2 bedroom with an office, study, kitchen, gallery & abundant storage. An elegant one-of-a-kind mesh of exposed conduit, stoic beams & manufacturing accoutrements coupled with modern innovations such as remote entry, elevator, functional built-ins, w/d, chefs' kitchen, cair plus a parking space. Welcome to the grass roots Mondo Condo community walkable to vast lifestyle & transportation resources distinct to Boston.
